summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Nego Talent Marketplace. All backend APIs (20/20 tests passed) and frontend features working correctly.
seed_data_creation: Database already seeded with 8 talents and 3 private content items via POST /api/seed
context_for_next_testing_agent: All features tested and working: Health API, Talents API (8 items with location data), Content API (3 locked items), Auth APIs (register, login, me). Frontend Hero section with Negotiate button (inverse hover state working), Talent section displaying 8 cards from API, Premium section showing 3 locked content cards. Navigation between sections works correctly.

backend: GET /api/talents - returns 8 talents with location data
GET /api/content - returns 3 locked private content items
POST /api/auth/register - creates new user and returns token
POST /api/auth/login - authenticates user and returns token
GET /api/auth/me - returns current user with valid token
frontend: Button hover state shows inverse colors (red bg -> transparent bg, white text -> red text)
Talent section loads and displays 8 talent cards from API
Premium section loads and displays 3 locked content cards from API
Navigation between sections (Home, Collection, Private Content) works
